Developer Terms of Use
des: With this skill you can listen live to Fabulous 1580 and 103.3, KCHA. We play the best of the 50s, 60s, and 70s. From our studios in Charles City, Iowa we will provide you the best oldies you could ever hope for as well as local sports and news! You can find out what song we are currently playing by telling Alexa, \"ask the fab oldies channel what song is currently playing.\"
